race.comment: PERMISSION GRANTED (4) Yes Yes Yes gelding from Rosie's Halo on debut for the Matt Dunn stable. Fitted with five solid trials and looks well placed from the low draw. CHOCECLAIR (8) now in the Sharon Croxford yard after disappointing in three career runs. Back in grade when a plugging fourth over 1210m at Moruya. Maps well and shapes as a likely improver here. DARLING TAKE CARE (9) resuming from a break. Placed in a recent trial. Opened last campaign with a third at Grafton over 1000m. In the mix. ZANJEER (3) returned from a spell with fair effort last start when seventh, beaten 2.75 lengths, at Eagle Farm over 1000m. Fitter and a hope.
